codeText: public EvaluationContext createEvaluationContext(ApplicationEvent event, Class<?> targetClass,_			Method method, Object[] args, BeanFactory beanFactory) {__		Method targetMethod = getTargetMethod(targetClass, method)__		EventExpressionRootObject root = new EventExpressionRootObject(event, args)__		MethodBasedEvaluationContext evaluationContext =_				new MethodBasedEvaluationContext(root, targetMethod, args, this.paramNameDiscoverer)__		if (beanFactory != null) {_			evaluationContext.setBeanResolver(new BeanFactoryResolver(beanFactory))__		}_		return evaluationContext__	}
